{"sha": "fb27d01922a5d7401959b95ce2c16cd02b7fac28", "node_id": "C_kwDOAAsO6NoAKGZiMjdkMDE5MjJhNWQ3NDAxOTU5Yjk1Y2UyYzE2Y2QwMmI3ZmFjMjg", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Yuki Okushi", "email": "jtitor@2k36.org", "date": "2022-10-09T15:09:41Z"}, "committer": {"name": "GitHub", "email": "noreply@github.com", "date": "2022-10-09T15:09:41Z"}, "message": "Rollup merge of #102799 - rol1510:issue-100421-fix, r=notriddle\n\nrustdoc: remove hover gap in file picker\n\nFixes #100421\n\nBefore:\n<img width=\"385\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194677087-fda2db3e-126d-47cf-8152-c554e3c25a54.png\">\n\nAfter:\n<img width=\"388\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194676774-7a50ace9-4060-492e-849a-ad85d9132630.png\">\n\nlonge module names also wrap nicely:\n<img width=\"389\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194678516-f2497b3a-8d50-439b-9d69-3fa9fb43b84d.png\">\n\nAlso if you zoom out very far, the arrows did move to the left, in relation to the text below. This is now also fixed.\n<img width=\"818\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194677652-cfdf129d-f5db-4f26-ac3c-3d0853e89619.png\">\n\nCSS doesn't have a lot of controll over the `::marker` element, so now the `::after` element is used to draw the arrows.\n\nNow the whole line is clickable wihtout gaps.", "tree": {"sha": "c9aecf63d858266497925683f69dc63bcf098dbe", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/c9aecf63d858266497925683f69dc63bcf098dbe"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/fb27d01922a5d7401959b95ce2c16cd02b7fac28", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsBcBAABCAAQBQJjQuQ1CRBK7hj4Ov3rIwAA2QsIAKhfCArGVVEseKCTKKKCIvDc\nc89jjBpHrZHzFvKcLpLhu1Q3zANggcL2mrD2ejkfxwXhQZtQ9Av7VAKlGDuhRSxd\nCP00p8u2NzjTHq0wVNJcM+4jTlf1gXAynROMxDgawGkMHJHo2MpuGAfKImh0IDWY\nTUCupVPEqUvjNo92XAaDD75dMbyFn/8nwBBX+RVuGwogMzmCQnbjPmIkA9vMZDth\njQf2AB0wbtmnVP2l1zG3HCxSoPJZn9nE7/dqnI86+UH2C8DCb+GOg5UaNkIKn5Us\ngtZyIkW8tCXFWGa3GebVg0mh4rMTnCoBmPxZuOBftO+Th57fezI+RwyNGe1ffDw=\n=8u9B\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n", "payload": "tree c9aecf63d858266497925683f69dc63bcf098dbe\nparent 38db483af750535774616810f1f8a4e6bdc17260\nparent 7fdce6498adf1bc337f6ab259af4aa9201dbc4a5\nauthor Yuki Okushi <jtitor@2k36.org> 1665328181 +0900\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1665328181 +0900\n\nRollup merge of #102799 - rol1510:issue-100421-fix, r=notriddle\n\nrustdoc: remove hover gap in file picker\n\nFixes #100421\n\nBefore:\n<img width=\"385\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194677087-fda2db3e-126d-47cf-8152-c554e3c25a54.png\">\n\nAfter:\n<img width=\"388\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194676774-7a50ace9-4060-492e-849a-ad85d9132630.png\">\n\nlonge module names also wrap nicely:\n<img width=\"389\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194678516-f2497b3a-8d50-439b-9d69-3fa9fb43b84d.png\">\n\nAlso if you zoom out very far, the arrows did move to the left, in relation to the text below. This is now also fixed.\n<img width=\"818\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29011024/194677652-cfdf129d-f5db-4f26-ac3c-3d0853e89619.png\">\n\nCSS doesn't have a lot of controll over the `::marker` element, so now the `::after` element is used to draw the arrows.\n\nNow the whole line is clickable wihtout gaps.\n"}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/fb27d01922a5d7401959b95ce2c16cd02b7fac28", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/fb27d01922a5d7401959b95ce2c16cd02b7fac28", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/fb27d01922a5d7401959b95ce2c16cd02b7fac28/comments", "author": {"login": "JohnTitor", "id": 25030997, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI1MDMwOTk3", "avatar_url": "h